Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.51,Pop,,0,0,0,,This beach is named
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.51,0:00:03.12,Pop,,0,0,0,,after {\c&H00FFFF&}seven{\c&HFFFFFF&} presidents. The
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.12,0:00:05.04,Pop,,0,0,0,,real number, maybe {\c&H00FFFF&}four.{\c&HFFFFFF&}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.04,0:00:07.16,Pop,,0,0,0,,Ulysses {\c&H00FFFF&}Grant{\c&HFFFFFF&} came first.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.16,0:00:08.12,Pop,,0,0,0,,He held cabinet meetings
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.12,0:00:09.13,Pop,,0,0,0,,on the porch and
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.13,0:00:10.27,Pop,,0,0,0,,played {\c&H00FFFF&}poker{\c&HFFFFFF&} with America's
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.27,0:00:11.93,Pop,,0,0,0,,wealthiest men every Friday
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.93,0:00:13.77,Pop,,0,0,0,,night. Then {\c&H00FFFF&}Garfield{\c&HFFFFFF&} was
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.77,0:00:15.40,Pop,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&}shot.{\c&HFFFFFF&} The bullet missed
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.40,0:00:16.94,Pop,,0,0,0,,every vital organ. It
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.94,0:00:18.31,Pop,,0,0,0,,was the {\c&H00FFFF&}infections{\c&HFFFFFF&} that
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.31,0:00:19.86,Pop,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&}killed{\c&HFFFFFF&} him. Volunteers laid
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.86,0:00:21.57,Pop,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&}3,200{\c&HFFFFFF&} feet of {\c&H00FFFF&}track{\c&HFFFFFF&}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.57,0:00:22.82,Pop,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&}overnight{\c&HFFFFFF&} by torch light
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.82,0:00:23.91,Pop,,0,0,0,,to bring a dying
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.91,0:00:25.00,Pop,,0,0,0,,president to the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:26.70,Pop,,0,0,0,,Today, a small tea
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.70,0:00:28.40,Pop,,0,0,0,,house still stands on
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.40,0:00:29.68,Pop,,0,0,0,,the church grounds ,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.68,0:00:31.55,Pop,,0,0,0,,built from those very
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.55,0:00:33.00,Pop,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&}railroad{\c&HFFFFFF&} ties. The original
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.00,0:00:34.04,Pop,,0,0,0,,red paint has faded
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.04,0:00:35.61,Pop,,0,0,0,,to pink after 140
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.61,0:00:37.72,Pop,,0,0,0,,years of shore weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.72,0:00:39.11,Pop,,0,0,0,,Woodrow {\c&H00FFFF&}Wilson{\c&HFFFFFF&} ran his
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.11,0:00:40.51,Pop,,0,0,0,,entire campaign from a
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.51,0:00:41.92,Pop,,0,0,0,,52 room beach house.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.92,0:00:43.52,Pop,,0,0,0,,His slogan, "He kept
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.52,0:00:45.12,Pop,,0,0,0,,us out of {\c&H00FFFF&}war."{\c&HFFFFFF&}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.12,0:00:46.21,Pop,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&}Five{\c&HFFFFFF&} months later, he
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.21,0:00:47.53,Pop,,0,0,0,,asked Congress to declare
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.53,0:00:49.10,Pop,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&}war{\c&HFFFFFF&} on Germany. {\c&H00FFFF&}Three{\c&HFFFFFF&}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.10,0:00:50.77,Pop,,0,0,0,,of the {\c&H00FFFF&}seven,{\c&HFFFFFF&} almost
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.77,0:00:52.14,Pop,,0,0,0,,certainly {\c&H00FFFF&}fiction.{\c&HFFFFFF&} But the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.14,0:00:53.22,Pop,,0,0,0,,stories they left behind
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.22,0:00:53.76,Pop,,0,0,0,,are real.
